import React from 'react'
import { DescText, MemberContainer, MemberImg, MemberLeftBox, MemberRightBox, NameTitle, RoleText } from './styles'

const MemberBox = () => {
  return (
    <MemberContainer>
        <MemberLeftBox>
            <MemberImg />
        </MemberLeftBox>
        <MemberRightBox>
            <NameTitle>Jan Huňař</NameTitle>
            <RoleText>Primáš</RoleText>
            <DescText>Vůdce našeho ansáblu</DescText>
        </MemberRightBox>
    </MemberContainer>
  )
}

export default MemberBox
